---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Hand-Arm & Whole-Body Vibration Assessments — Bureau Veritas AVOH"
  description="HAV and WBV assessments, VEMS vibration exposure management, compliance with CoVAWR, HAVS risk assessments for onshore and offshore facilities."
>
  <Hero
    title="Hand-Arm & Whole-Body Vibration"
    subtitle="Vibration risk assessments, production of management plans and auditing to help you comply with the Control of Vibration at Work Regulations."
    image="construction.jpg"
    imageAlt="Construction site vibration"
  />

  <Breadcrumbs current="Hand-Arm &amp; Whole-Body Vibration" />

  <article class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-bv-navy mb-6">Control of Vibration at Work Regulations 2005</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Hand-Arm Vibration Syndrome (HAVS) is the most commonly reported disease under RIDDOR. Over-exposure of hands to high levels of vibration can lead to permanent disability of equipment operators.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          The Control of Vibration at Work Regulations (CoVAWR) place a duty on employers to assess and manage vibration risks from vibrating tools and equipment, extending to whole-body vibration experienced when seated or standing in high-vibration areas. Whether an industrial plant, offshore installation or vessel, we can help manage occupational vibration and achieve compliance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-bv-navy mb-6">Our Services</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {[
            'Assessment of employee exposure to Hand-Arm Vibration (HAV) and Whole-Body Vibration (WBV)',
            'Compilation of hand-held equipment datasheets and associated time to achieve regulatory exposure action values',
            'Provision of vibration management plans for regulatory compliance',
            'Workplace risk assessments',
            'Identification of tools or processes likely to induce HAVS',
            'Measures to reduce occupational vibration',
            'Training of local operators in assessing vibration',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-bv-teal flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-bv-navy mb-6">VEMS — Vibration Exposure Management System</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Bureau Veritas developed VEMS (Vibration Exposure Management System) to simplify the assessment process. It provides a user-friendly management system allowing employers to monitor personnel exposure over time and avoid exposure in excess of regulatory action values.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          {[
            'Calculation of personnel vibration exposure levels',
            'Monitoring of exposure over time',
            'Recording facilities for ongoing compliance',
            'Key Performance Indicators for vibration risk',
          ].map((benefit) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-bv-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">{benefit}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-bv-navy/5 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-bv-navy mb-4">Why Choose Bureau Veritas?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          We provide cost-effective solutions to help you meet your regulatory requirements. These services can be combined as part of a multi-disciplinary survey including occupational noise and occupational hygiene assessments.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>

  <ContactSection />

  <Breadcrumbs current="Hand-Arm &amp; Whole-Body Vibration" />
</Layout>
